      building enterprise applications, distributed systems and cloud-native platforms.

    </p>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-400 leading-9">

      Specialized in .NET, Azure, Microservices, Domain-Driven Design (DDD),
      CQRS and Event-Driven Architecture. Passionate about software architecture,
      modernization initiatives and AI-powered solutions that deliver measurable
      business value.

    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">

